<subSubSection id="20FCCEE55B028108FF4FFBD8FB0E1F27" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="68599D6E5B028108FF4FFBD8FB0E1F27" blockId="21.[151,1436,1070,1349]" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FF4FFBD8FEE11E2B" bold="true" box="[151,269,1071,1097]" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">Remarks:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FEC1FBD8FDE71E2A" authorityName="Buckton" authorityYear="1903" box="[281,523,1071,1097]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Hyphinoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctorum">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FEC1FBD8FDE71E2A" box="[281,523,1071,1097]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">Hyphinoe punctorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is proposed as a 
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FD3CFBD9FC491E2B" bold="true" box="[740,933,1070,1097]" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">junior synonym</emphasis>
of 
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FC0CFBD8FB7B1E2A" baseAuthorityName="Fairmaire" baseAuthorityYear="1846" box="[980,1175,1071,1097]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Eualthe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctum">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FC0CFBD8FB7B1E2A" box="[980,1175,1071,1097]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">Eualthe punctum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on the original descriptions and illustrations. Fairmaire (1946) and 
<bibRefCitation id="0C77E09F5B028108FD00FBA4FC641E0F" author="Buckton" box="[728,904,1107,1133]" firstAuthor="Buckton" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" refId="ref11986" refString="Buckton, G. B. (1903) A Monograph of the Membracidae. Lovell Reeve, London, 296 pp." type="book" year="1903">Buckton (1903)</bibRefCitation>
characterized their respective species as having the following combination of features: an ochraceous-yellow pronotum with one pair of brown spot at each side; suprahumeral horns somewhat acute and divergent; and posterior process exceeding the apex of forewings. 
<bibRefCitation id="0C77E09F5B028108FAE5FB6CFF0E1EBB" author="Buckton" firstAuthor="Buckton" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" refId="ref11986" refString="Buckton, G. B. (1903) A Monograph of the Membracidae. Lovell Reeve, London, 296 pp." type="book" year="1903">Buckton (1903)</bibRefCitation>
discussed a possible synonymy between these species, stating that 
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FC0CFB48FB2D1EBA" authorityName="Buckton" authorityYear="1903" box="[980,1217,1215,1241]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Hyphinoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctorum">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FC0CFB48FB2D1EBA" box="[980,1217,1215,1241]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">Hyphinoe punctorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
could be “a variety of 
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FF6DFB14FE4E1E9E" authorityName="Fairmaire" authorityYear="1846" box="[181,418,1251,1277]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Hemiptycha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctum">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FF6DFB14FE4E1E9E" box="[181,418,1251,1277]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">Hemiptycha punctum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” (p. 124). 
<bibRefCitation id="0C77E09F5B028108FDC3FB14FD2C1E9F" author="Goding" box="[539,704,1251,1277]" firstAuthor="Goding" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" pagination="197 - 330" refId="ref12430" refString="Goding, F. W. (1929) The Membracidae of South America and The Antilles. IV. Subfamilies Hoplophorioninae, Darninae, Smiliinae, Tragopinae (Homoptera). Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 55 (3), 197 - 330." type="journal article" year="1929">Goding (1929)</bibRefCitation>
treated this species as 
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FC65FB14FBC61E9F" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1869" box="[957,1066,1251,1277]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Bubalopa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FC65FB14FBC61E9F" box="[957,1066,1251,1277]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">Bubalopa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on his interpretation of the literature, and 
<bibRefCitation id="0C77E09F5B028108FEEDFAF0FDE51F43" author="Funkhouser" box="[309,521,1286,1313]" firstAuthor="Funkhouser" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" pagination="1 - 383" refId="ref12408" refString="Funkhouser, W. D. (1951) Homoptera Family Membracidae. Genera Insectorum, 208, 1 - 383." type="journal article" year="1951">Funkhouser (1951)</bibRefCitation>
incorrectly treated 
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FD05FAF0FC9A1F42" authorityName="Buckton" authorityYear="1903" box="[733,886,1287,1312]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Hyphinoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctorum">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FD05FAF0FC9A1F42" box="[733,886,1287,1312]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">H. punctorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FBE8FAF0FB711F43" authorityName=", Stal" authorityYear="1869" box="[1072,1181,1287,1313]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Bubalopa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="furcata">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FBE8FAF0FB711F43" box="[1072,1181,1287,1313]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">B. furcata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This misidentification hindered the accurate determination of 
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FD96FADCFD061F26" authorityName="Buckton" authorityYear="1903" box="[590,746,1323,1348]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Hyphinoe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctorum">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FD96FADCFD061F26" box="[590,746,1323,1348]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">H. punctorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as well as 
<taxonomicName id="AFE6E6ED5B028108FCBDFADCFC3E1F27" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1869" box="[869,978,1323,1349]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Bubalopa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="550" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="5A92417C5B028108FCBDFADCFC3E1F27" box="[869,978,1323,1349]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="550">Bubalopa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and its constituent taxa.
</paragraph>
